text: Sergey Valeryevich Aksyonov (, ; born 26 November 1972) is a Russian politician. Aksyonov is the Prime Minister of Crimea. He is the first Prime Minister of Crimea since it gained independence in March 2014. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Crimea Category:Specially Designated Nationals and Blocked Persons List Category:Current national leaders
